name: Magic Mirror
description:
Hold your face in front of the magic mirror and peek into a world of wonders and fantasies. Meet your doppelgangers and your dark versions in alternate realities. Don't stare too hard into the mirror, or your mind will contract glitches of multiple realities rendering you unable to distinguish between this and that reality. 

Keep a shiny object in your hand ready to combat any mysterious entities trying to enter into our universe. Hold still and fight back. Otherwise, relax and enjoy the experience. 

Digital Painting
1498x1498 pixels

2016
